description="If you see the silhouette of the Sunset Tower from a distance, turn around. Yes, the apartment complex down below looks clean and has plenty of space, but the stairwells of that 17-story building are a one-way trip. Those who tried to isolate themselves up there barricaded the hallways by throwing everything they had—cabinets, sofas, tables—but it was no use. The place has turned into a vertical slaughterhouse. Every floor is clogged with debris and covered in dried blood. If you decide to go in, know that you won’t even have room to run from the infected."
